A quadrant of space in the [[Corellian system/Legends|Corellian system]], '''Corellia's Own''' was perhaps the most peaceful and orderly area in the entire system, including most of the cities on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] itself. Patrolled strictly by [[Corellian Security Force|CorSec]] under the direct order of the [[Diktat]], it was a sector unsullied by the presence of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] even at its height. Traveled mostly by peaceful freighters and civilian ships, the Corellia's Own quadrant provided safe, speedy travel to the Double Worlds of [[Talus/Legends|Talus]] and [[Tralus/Legends|Tralus]] and [[Centerpoint Station]].

